headline: ‘Our New Favorites’: Raymond James Selects 2 Stocks as New Top Picks
summary: We’ve now moved through the third year of a bull market that began in the fall of 2022, following the breakthrough moment when ChatGPT showcased the potential of generative AI. In 2025, the S&P 500 advanced ~16.5%, while the tech-heavy Nasdaq climbed about 20.5%. Looking ahead, a number of factors are lining up, ready to give support to further growth.
